name: PROUDLY COMPANY Soft & Absorbent Diapers
description: The PROUDLY Soft & Absorbent Diapers help keep leaks locked-in when your littlest love is movin’ and groovin’. Designed with superior stretch for growth spurts and transition sizing, ultra-absorbency, comfort fit, and a wetness indicator. Because bum care is skin care, we’ve enriched the inner layer with shea butter to add moisture for melanated skin. Made with love with our signature “Littlest Love” print featuring the beautiful range of melanated skin tone hearts. Use as a part of a Bum Care Routine with PROUDLY Gentle Touch Baby Wipes and Soothing Diaper Cream. Co-founded by Gabrielle Union and Dwyane Wade, PROUDLY is an affordable baby care line designed for babies of color. Melanated skin of all diverse hues can be more prone to dryness, eczema, and acne and our littlest loves deserve products made with their unique needs in mind. Each product is co-designed by a Black dermatologist who has studied and hand-selected ingredients that nourish melanated skin—and includes absolutely No Sketchy Stuff!—ever. We are proud to be Black-owned, Black-founded, and operated diversely by people of color. Welcome to a world of baby care made for us, by us and a home for you.

name: The Honest Company Clean Conscious Disposable Diapers Stripe Safari & Seeing Spots
description: Introducing our best diapering experience ever! New Clean Conscious Diapers are designed with safe, plant-based materials, a wetness indicator (so you know when it’s time for a fresh one), enhanced blowout protection, and advanced absorption for dry, healthy-looking booties. Plus, a secure, comfy fit for less sag + more swag.Our Clean Conscious Diapers were mindfully designed with features for each stage of your babe’s diapering journey. Grow up with Honest!What Makes A Clean Conscious Diaper?To make the core of the diaper, we harvest wood from sustainably managed pine + spruce trees in Scandinavia, which is then turned into fluff pulp at a Swedish mill using totally chlorine-free processing – aka no dioxins (toxic chemicals) in our waterwayWe don't add latex, fragrance, or parabensWe use a 100% plant-based backsheet, and our new, more efficient design reduces the amount of material used in each diaperOur diapers are cruelty-free and never tested on animalsOur diaper boxes are made from 100% PCR post recycled consumer cardboard (aka they’re 100% recyclable) – that means no new trees cut down and no landfill, if recycled How To Use:Lie your babe on their back on a safe, clean surface and gently lift them to place the diaper under their bum. Bring the diaper front over + up to your babe’s tummy and fasten the tabs securely. To minimize leaks, make sure the leg cuffs are pulled out, and not tucked in.Caring Caution: To avoid suffocation, keep this packaging away from babies + children. Choking may result from anything babies put in their mouths. To avoid the risk of choking, don’t allow babies to tear the diaper. Discard any torn or or damaged diapers. Like any piece of clothing, diapers are flammable.

name: Charlie Banana Reusable Swim Diaper with Snaps - (Select Size & Pattern)
description: At Charlie Banana, we care for your baby and our planet at the same time. Our reusable and washable swim diapers with snaps on both sides feature our signature softness, a snug fit, and lightweight waterproof materials that protect your baby's delicate skin without swelling in the water. Additionally, our super soft inner lining is made from plant-based TENCEL® Lyocell fibers, so that only the softest materials touch your little one's skin.In the box, you'll find one reusable and washable swim diaper with waist snaps, a waterproof outer lining, and a soft TENCEL® lyocell inner lining. Our swim diapers come in four sizes (small, medium, large, and X-large), so you can select the perfect size for your baby. Simply:1. Use the diaper,2. Rinse it,3. Toss it in the wash,4. Reuse again and again!There are multiple benefits of Charlie Banana reusable and washable swim diapers:• Side-snaps for easy-on and easy-off. Even when wet or dirty, our swim diapers with side-snaps work together with the wide elastic back, and leg elastics to contain solids and prevent leaks, as well as making changes quick and easy. All the fun and comfort, without the mess!• Lightweight comfort with no swelling. With waterproof, breathable, and quick-drying fabric, our swim diaper provides lightweight comfort that doesn't swell when wet, so your baby can move freely in the water.• Long-lasting and fun prints. Made from long-lasting, high-quality materials; they also come in cute prints just like a swimsuit, with colors that last, even after multiple washes.Charlie Banana products are made with your baby’s world in mind. When caring for our planet, we don’t just talk the talk; we walk the walk by donating 1% of our sales to support environmental and conservation causes.

name: PROUDLY COMPANY Moisture Layering Bath & Body Gift Set - 3ct
description: When it comes to supporting dry, sensitive skin, moisture is everything. The Moisture Layering Gift Set is a go-to for moisture-boosting, hydrating, nourishing care for your littlest love's extra-special skin. With our dermatologist-advised moisture layering routine on the back of package, any caregiver will be able to impart lasting moisture on dry, sensitive skin.The PROUDLY Mositure Layering 3-Piece Gift Set Includes:The PROUDLY Hydrating Baby Lotion in Lavender Chamomile is a go-to moisturizer for melanated babies. Replenishing jojoba oil moisturizes while hydrating shea butter deeply nourishes thirsty skin. It's lightweight and non-greasy for everyday application. The lavender chamomile scent is natural and gentle at less than 1% concentration to calm your littlest love (and you!) before bedtime or naptime.The PROUDLY Nourishing Oil is a replenishing blend of premium oils, squalane, and vitamin E to layer and lock-in lasting moisture for melanated skin. With only 5 ingredients, it is perfect from head and hair, to toe. Use as the last step of a moisture routine, as a pre-bath massage oil, or as part of a cradle cap treatment routine for scalp—and leave your littlest love with a touchable glow.The PROUDLY All Over Balm is an ultra-nourishing, multi-use balm enriched with mango butter and a blend of natural, premium oils to target stubborn dry spots and soothe itchy, irritated and sensitive melanated skin. Saturate elbows, knees, hands, and feet and every curve in between to provide deep moisture. Use a thin layer on your littlest love’s bum, folds, and creases to help prevent irritation from diaper rash. Great for the whole family—don’t forget your lips and cuticles! Tip: to begin, break through the top layer of the balm. Balm will be thick at first, so massage between fingers or hands to warm for a smooth, silky finish.

name: Frida Baby Fart Freeing Essentials - 11ct
description: Trapped farts are a pain in the gas. Tackle your baby's tummy troubles hands-on with Fart Freeing Essentials. Release gas and calm colic instantly with Windi the Gaspasser, a natural doctor-invented solution that does not require ingestion of any drops or medication. Most pediatric professionals are familiar with the method of using a rectal thermometer to relieve gas, colic, and constipation, and the Windi is designed specifically for this purpose. The soft, pliable, hollow tube features a rounded tip that is long enough to reach past the muscle that prevents the release of the gas, and also has a parent-proof stopper to prevent an insertion too far. Designed to be safe and effective, the Windi cannot harm your baby if used as instructed. And when baby's fussy from trapped gas in their tummy, try a belly massage with Gassy Belly Rub, a balm that's gentle on skin but tough on toots. Made with newborn-safe ingredients, Gassy Belly Rub can be used for a soothing nightly ritual to help calm your little one into sleep time. Just rub on, massage in, and get the gas flowin'. Use Windi and Gassy Belly Rub on their own or together to get a big release - so you can finally get some relief.

name: Boppy Original Nursing Suppor Nursing Pillow - Floral Stripes
description: This Boppy nursing pillow provides ergonomic support for breastfeeding, bottle feeding, and bonding. The c-shaped design allows for multiple feeding styles—cradle, cross cradle, football hold and bottle feeding. Aids positioning for a better latch and back relief. Machine washable for easy cleaning with removeable pillow cover for added ease. The average nursing mom spends over 35 hours per week breastfeeding. Get the tools for the job with the Boppy Original Support Nursing Pillow. The beltless design allows for an easy, one-handed placement with no fuss, and the Miracle Middle panel provides a seam-free connection with your body for a more comfortable fit for c-sections or stomach tenderness after birth. This award-winning Boppy nursing pillow is a registry must-have and a parent favorite. Small enough to easily fit in your rocking chair or glider, but big enough to give the support you need. Support for you and baby with hypoallergenic fiber fill and a removable cover to help keep your breastfeeding pillow cleaner longer. A variety of Boppy Nursing Pillow Covers to fit your style are sold separately, from cotton blends to organics, so you always have backup on laundry day. Designed for your baby's adult-supervised awake-time. This product is not for sleep. Thank you to the millions of parents who trust Boppy. Looking for extended sizes? Check out the Boppy Best Latch Support Nursing Pillow or the Boppy Anywhere Support Nursing Pillow for a perfect fit. This product should never be used for sleep. Our mission is to keep you feeling comfortable and confident with your decision to choose Boppy for high quality products, expert third party testing, and clear messaging. The AAP Safe Sleep Guidelines state that a baby should never be put to sleep with any pillow or plush product. Newborns should always be put to sleep on their back on a firm, flat surface free from loose blankets, pillows, stuffed toys, bumpers, and other soft items. Please always use products as intended.

name: My Brest Friend Twin Nursing Pillow - Horizon
description: After years of thorough research and real-life testing, the My Brest Friend nursing pillow is specifically designed to make breastfeeding more comfortable. Its supportive backrest encourages good posture during breastfeeding and prevents neck and shoulder strain, too. Also great at minimizing strain at the elbows and wrists, so you can focus all your attention on your little one. Innovative shape keeps baby close. My Brest friend boasts a unique shape and is the only pillow that fits snuggly against the wearer, eliminating the gap that most crescent-shaped nursing pillows have. This is especially important to facilitate proper latching for consistent feedings. Keep baby safe and sound and held securely in place on our firm and flat pillow throughout the entire nursing session. Keep all your maternity supplies and accessories easily within reach in the Super-convenient side pocket. Store extra bottles, nipple cream or even your smartphone to avoid getting up in the middle of nursing and disrupting baby. Wrap around design provides welcome support to your weary back and sore shoulders. My Brest friend nursing pillow surrounds your body for the ideal position for baby. Clever silent-release straps lets you slip away quietly when your newborn nods off and unlatches without waking the babe. My Brest friend strives to provide new mothers with the most intuitive and useful maternity products on the market. We are proud to be among the most preferred brands for lactation consultants and mothers alike and keep the comfort of mother and child at the forefront of everything we create.

name: Aveeno Baby Soothing Bath Treatment - 3.75oz - 5ct
description: Aveeno Baby Eczema Therapy Soothing Bath Treatment helps relieve minor skin irritation and itching caused by rashes, eczema, poison ivy, poison oak, poison sumac, or insect bites. From the dermatologist and pediatrician-recommended brand, this baby bath treatment is indicated to relieve dry, itchy, irritated skin and is accepted by the National Eczema Association. The unique formula of this tear-free and allergy-tested baby eczema therapy bath combines natural colloidal oatmeal skin protectant with a special moisturizer to help provide baby with dry skin relief. When dispersed in water, the ultra-fine powder forms a milky soothing bath that also works as a natural, soap-free cleanser and is gentle enough for delicate skin. After bathing, your baby's skin becomes softer and smoother, and dry irritated skin is relieved. Aveeno Baby Eczema Therapy Soothing Bath Treatment is gentle on eyes and free of steroids, soap, parabens, phthalates, phenoxyethanol and fragrances.

Gentle enough for everyday use on babies' sensitive skin, this hypoallergenic baby eczema balm combines colloidal oatmeal skin protectant and ceramide to help strengthen the skin's moisture barrier and help prevent recurrence of extra dry skin from eczema. The first and only nighttime balm formulated with Colloidal Oatmeal, this eczema therapy balm has been awarded the National Eczema Association Seal of Approval and intensely moisturizes and soothes skin so your baby will feel relief when applied. Give your baby dry skin relief without the greasy feeling with this body balm that is free of steroids, fragrances, parabens, phthalates and phenoxyethanol and helps relieve dry, itchy skin due to eczema. Aveeno is recommended by pediatricians and dermatologists.

When it comes to your baby, comfort and safety are always top of mind. With Dove Baby Eczema Care Soothing Cream, you can soothe your baby's skin and rest easy knowing you're using safe, gentle ingredients designed just for a baby's sensitive skin. name: Charlie Banana Reusable Swim Diaper with Snaps - (Select Size & Pattern)
description: At Charlie Banana, we care for your baby and our planet at the same time. Our reusable and washable swim diapers with snaps on both sides feature our signature softness, a snug fit, and lightweight waterproof materials that protect your baby's delicate skin without swelling in the water. We use only safe materials, rigorously tested for harmful substances, and certified under STANDARD 100 by OEKO-TEX®. Additionally, our super soft inner lining is made from plant-based TENCEL® Lyocell fibers, so that only the softest materials touch your little one's skin.In the box, you'll find one reusable and washable swim diaper with waist snaps, a waterproof outer lining, and a soft TENCEL® lyocell inner lining. Our swim diapers come in four sizes (small, medium, large, and X-large), so you can select the perfect size for your baby. Simply:1. Use the diaper,2. Rinse it,3. Toss it in the wash,4. Reuse again and again!There are multiple benefits of Charlie Banana reusable and washable swim diapers:• Side-snaps for easy-on and easy-off. Even when wet or dirty, our swim diapers with side-snaps work together with the wide elastic back, and leg elastics to contain solids and prevent leaks, as well as making changes quick and easy. All the fun and comfort, without the mess!• Lightweight comfort with no swelling. With waterproof, breathable, and quick-drying fabric, our swim diaper provides lightweight comfort that doesn't swell when wet, so your baby can move freely in the water.• Long-lasting and fun prints. Made from long-lasting, high-quality materials; they also come in cute prints just like a swimsuit, with colors that last, even after multiple washes.Charlie Banana products are made with your baby’s world in mind. When caring for our planet, we don’t just talk the talk; we walk the walk by donating 1% of our sales to support environmental and conservation causes.

Moisturizing face & body balm recommended by pediatricians & dermatologists is steroid, fragrance, paraben, phthalate & phenoxyethanol free. An independent clinical has shown Aveeno Baby Eczema Therapy Balm is suitable to use on newborn's skin as early as the second day of life, before the onset of rashes and dryness.

description: Eucerin Baby Eczema Relief Body Cream is a clinically proven moisturizing formula that relieves dry, itchy, eczema-prone skin. This fast-absorbing baby eczema cream is formulated with Colloidal Oatmeal (a skin protectant), Ceramide-3 to lock in moisture, and Licorice Root Extract to help soothe irritated skin. Eucerin Baby Eczema Relief Body Cream delivers 24 hour hydration and helps to strengthen the skin's protective barrier. This Eucerin eczema relief baby cream is free of fragrance and steroids, and is gentle enough for daily use on your baby's delicate skin. Eucerin Baby eczema cream is appropriate for use on adults, children, and babies 3 months and older. In a clinical study, with daily use, 4 out of 5 children remained flare-free for 6 months (1). To use, gently massage Eucerin eczema baby cream on baby's skin as needed. (1) J Drugs Dermatol Children’s Clinical (2015);14478-479

name: Boudreaux's Butt Paste Baby Diaper Rash Cream Maximum Strength - 4oz
description: Developed by a pharmacist and father of four, Boudreaux's Butt Paste Brand has been trusted for over 40 years by pediatricians and parents to help protect irritated skin due to diaper rash and to instantly seal out wetness. name: Boppy Best Latch Nursing Pillow - Gray Leaf Stripe
description: The Boppy Best Latch Nursing Support was created with a lactation consultant and designed to support many body types. The thoughtful design offers a wide, padded, adjustable belt, a large easy-close buckle, a flexible fit, and added height and depth to provide ergonomic support while nursing. This breastfeeding support is two-sided to give you the option between a firm, contoured foam side that helps position baby for an easier latch while nursing and a plush side for cozy comfort. Perfect for nursing or bottle feeding. The foam insert provides a firm surface, it is also gently contoured to help baby naturally roll into “belly-to-belly and nose-to-nipple” position. The edges are rounded, sloping with your body so no hard edges dig into your mid-section, while the outer edge is slightly raised providing a wall that helps position baby for a successful latch. Designed for every body, this Boppy Nursing Support features a wider middle that is great for a larger waist and bigger breasts. The padded waist belt supports plus sized users by keeping the support in place and creates a tighter hug around petite bodies. The added height is perfect for those who are tall, have a long torso, or are flatter chested. All of these features help to better fit your body and help position baby, so you get a better latch when nursing. A healthy latch can reduce discomfort and increase nursing success. When dealing with milk or those less cute messes, simply remove the water-resistant, wipeable foam insert and toss the rest of the support into the washing machine and dryer. And don’t worry…the high quality, quick-drying fibers will not get misshapen in the wash. This product is for feeding support only. Thank you to the millions of parents who trust Boppy! #BoppyLove

description: The Butterfly SwaddleTM is a one of a kind sleep training system serving as an organic swaddle wrap and/or a transitional sleep sack. Boasting patented mesh "butterfly wings" located under the sleeves of the sleep sack, the wings gently slow the startle reflex while still allowing purposeful arm movements for comfort. Rayon from Bamboo are moisture wicking; and organic french terry cotton (super soft and breathable), will help keep your delicate baby safe and comfortable.

name: Boppy Original Support Nursing Pillow - Watercolor Flowers
description: This Boppy nursing pillow provides ergonomic support for breastfeeding, bottle feeding, and bonding. The c-shaped design allows for multiple feeding styles—cradle, cross cradle, football hold and bottle feeding. Aids positioning for a better latch and back relief. Machine washable for easy cleaning with removeable pillow cover for added ease. The average nursing mom spends over 35 hours per week breastfeeding. Get the tools for the job with the Boppy Original Support Nursing Pillow. The beltless design allows for an easy, one-handed placement with no fuss, and the Miracle Middle panel provides a seam-free connection with your body for a more comfortable fit for c-sections or stomach tenderness after birth. This award-winning Boppy nursing pillow is a registry must-have and a parent favorite. Small enough to easily fit in your rocking chair or glider, but big enough to give the support you need. Support for you and baby with hypoallergenic fiber fill and a removable cover to help keep your breastfeeding pillow cleaner longer. A variety of Boppy Nursing Pillow Covers to fit your style are sold separately, from cotton blends to organics, so you always have backup on laundry day. Designed for your baby's adult-supervised awake-time. This product is not for sleep. Thank you to the millions of parents who trust Boppy. Looking for extended sizes? Check out the Boppy Best Latch Support Nursing Pillow or the Boppy Anywhere Support Nursing Pillow for a perfect fit. This product should never be used for sleep. Our mission is to keep you feeling comfortable and confident with your decision to choose Boppy for high quality products, expert third party testing, and clear messaging. The AAP Safe Sleep Guidelines state that a baby should never be put to sleep with any pillow or plush product. Newborns should always be put to sleep on their back on a firm, flat surface free from loose blankets, pillows, stuffed toys, bumpers, and other soft items. Please always use products as intended.

name: Charlie Banana One-size Reusable Cloth Diaper with 2 Reusable Inserts (Select Color)
description: At Charlie Banana, we’re all about caring for your baby and our planet at the same time. Our unique, reusable cloth diapers are designed with our signature edge-to-edge softness to help protect your baby’s delicate skin. We use only safe, long-lasting materials rigorously tested for harmful substances by independent laboratories and certified under STANDARD 100 by OEKO-TEX®. With the Charlie Banana one-size diaper pack, you’ll get six one-size reusable cloth diaper shells (with a fluffy fleece lining) and twelve deluxe reusable diaper inserts. You can use them in three ways:1. The pocket option. Put one or two reusable inserts into the pocket of your cloth diaper shell. 2. Insert on top. Place the insert atop the diaper's inner lining rather than inside the pocket for slightly easier cleanup. 3. The hybrid approach. Need super fast cleanup? Try the hybrid option and place a disposable insert (not included) atop the pocket. You can use any of our washable, reusable inserts or disposable diaper inserts with the same diaper shell. And our diapers aren’t just made from long-lasting, high-quality materials; they’re also vibrant and colorful, with fun designs to bring joy to your baby, like a cactus print, cute pineapples, and more!There are even more benefits of Charlie Banana reusable cloth diapers:• One size is all you need. Thanks to our easy waist snaps and patented flexible sizing system (which uses elastic to adjust just like a bra strap), our one-size diaper system grows with your baby from birth to 36 months.• Easily prevent leaks. You get the perfect fit to avoid leaks with wide back elastic, waist snaps, and inner leg elastics.• Easy to clean. Our reusable inserts are machine washable, and because you can remove them from the cloth diaper shell, everything dries faster. Or, you can use a disposable liner to catch the mess for even easier cleanup.We designed Charlie Banana diapers with your baby’s world in mind. When caring for our planet, we don’t just talk the talk; we walk the walk and donate 1% of our sales to support environmental and conservation causes.

Microfiber is a fast absorber designed to rest closest to your baby's skin (beneath the microfleece sleeve); hemp is a stable absorber and pairs perfectly behind the microfiber to add more absorbency and prevent compression leaking.

Included in this baby bedding set is a snuggle sleeper (baby wearable blanket) which is recommended for safe sleep. It is made of 100% cotton in heather gray with an appliqued moon and stars. name: Lambs & Ivy Happy Jungle Pink/White Safari Nursery 5-Piece Crib Bedding Set
description: The five-piece nursery crib bedding set includes one quilt, one breathable 100% cotton fitted crib sheet, one crib skirt, one rectangular throw pillow, and a complete set of wall decals. This Happy Jungle features a spotted leopard dangling on a large tree branch along with a mommy and baby lion. The baby lion sits happily on the back of a white plush minky elephant with gray embroidered ears. A mommy and baby tiger are close by walking on scattered pink and gray flowers. Trendy pink pom poms decorate the border of this high-quality, luxurious cotton sateen quilt. The image of the elephant with the lion on its back shows some of the luxurious quilt detail. The breathable 100% cotton fitted crib sheet includes all the Happy Jungle animals along with trees, flowers, and leaves. The fitted crib sheet has elastic all the way around ensuring a safe and secure fit on a standard size crib mattress measuring 52" x 28". The crib skirt is shirred and includes three rows of colorful pom pom trim on the front panel. It has a 14 ½” drop. A pretty rectangle throw pillow with pom pom trim is also included in this set. It measures 16” X 10” X 3”. It opens in the back allowing for washing the pillowcase separately for easy care. Complete this amazing collection with a set of custom wall decals. There are four sheets of 12” X 18” with a total of 35 die-cut decals. Included is a 30” tall gray tree, a 16” long elephant, a spotted black and white leopard who loves resting on a tree branch, and a cute baby lion on the elephant’s back. Add to that a baby tiger and a cute tropical bird. Wall decals are a great way to add a mural-like designer touch to your baby’s room. They are easy to apply and will not harm your walls.

Finish your nursery with the other matching accessories such as the Musical Crib Mobile Toy, Spike the Dinosaur Plush Stuffed Animal, a Fitted Crib Sheet, or Wall Decals (all sold separately). name: Lambs & Ivy Bow Wow Gray/Tan Dog/Puppy Nursery 3-Piece Baby Crib Bedding Set
description: This three-piece canine themed nursery crib bedding set includes one quilt, one breathable 100% cotton fitted crib sheet and one crib skirt. A combination of upscale fabrics was used to create this playful nursery collection. They include faux fur (polyester), minky, twill print, suede, ribbed velour, herringbone, windowpane print, houndstooth print and plaid. The patchwork quilt includes six appliqued dogs. Included are Terriers, French Bulldogs, English Pointers, Labs, Dobermans, Dalmatians and doggy bones and treats. The crib skirt adds the finishing touch to your child’s crib. The upper panel is a cotton-poly windowpane twill, and the lower panel is gray herringbone. There is a solid gray twill flange in between. It has a 14 ½” drop and everything is machine washable for easy care.

name: Esembly Cloth Diaper Inner Organic Cotton Reusable Diaper - (Select Size)
description: Esembly reusable cloth diapers are made up of two parts: an absorbent Inner and a waterproof Outer (sold separately). Esembly Inners are made of super soft and thirsty certified organic cotton. Inners are designed with a unique butterfly shaped core to maximize absorbency while still allowing water and detergent to access all layers of the diaper for a deep and thorough cleaning and efficient drying.Esembly Inners come in two sizes and are made to grow with your baby. The waist snaps allow for adjustments to accommodate expanding bellies, while the rippled core and stretchy elastic at the legs will expand as your babe gets taller. Inners are designed to be worn with an Esembly Outer (sold separately) for waterproofing and containment. Here’s how it works:• Put a fresh Inner on your baby at each change.• Cover the Inner with a waterproof Outer to make a complete diaper.• Change your baby every 2-3 hours, or immediately if poop is detected.• To accommodate long nighttime sleep stretches, boost the absorbency of your diaper with an Overnighter (sold separately).• When soiled, set aside in the Day Bag or Pail Pouch until laundry day.If cloth diapering full-time, you’ll want to have 24 Inners and 6 Outers. Inners require laundering after each use, whereas Outers can be used multiple times before washing.Launder your Inners and Outers every 2-3 days using Esembly Washing Powder (or similar clean-rinsing detergent) as per Esembly’s super-simple, step-by-step wash instructions.

description: Looking for a better alternative to disposable diapers that’s easy to use and will save you money while saving the planet? Look no further than Esembly! The Esembly line of cloth diaper products and accessories provide families with everything they need to diaper sustainably - from organic, “blowout-proof” diapers and skincare, to upcycled storage bags and specially-formulated diaper cleaning detergent. Don’t be! The Esembly founders spent over a decade washing cloth diapers for their busy NYC diaper service and know exactly how to make diaper laundry easy enough for any sleep-deprived parent to master. All it takes is 2 loads of laundry per week following their super-simple, step-by-step instructions (included with each kit).The Esembly Try-It Kit is available in 4 exclusive to Target prints.

name: Lambs & Ivy Watercolor Pastel Pink/Mint Rainbow 5-Piece Baby Crib Bedding Set

Complete this charming nursery with wall decals featuring seven watercolor rainbows with a hand-painted look. They add a designer touch to a feature wall in the nursery. This beautiful crib bedding set is a top baby registry pick and makes a wonderful baby shower gift as well.

name: Lambs & Ivy Baby Jungle Animals 4-Piece Gray/White/Taupe Crib Bedding Set
description: This four-piece nursery baby bedding set includes one quilt, one 100% cotton fitted crib sheet, one crib skirt and a complete set of wall decals. The neutral color palette of gray, taupe, tan, cream and charcoal gray makes it perfect for baby boys and girls. The quilt features a 28” tall giraffe made with a textured chevron patterned minky. His mane is a thick eyelash trim in gray and his tassel tail is made of gray yarn. His feet are a charcoal gray corduroy. Our sweet baby elephant is made with gray minky, he has a 3-dimensional ear with embroidered stitching and a yarn tassel tail. A friendly toucan is appliqued in gray corduroy with cream fur minky and stands comfortably on an outlined tree branch. Up at the top of the quilt is a fuzzy, smiling, gray sloth hanging from a brown tree branch. His name is Speedy, and he is sure to delight your little adventurer. The 100% breathable cotton fitted crib sheet features giraffes, elephants, toucans, sloths and small trees and branches on a crisp white ground. The 100% cotton fitted crib sheet has elastic all around ensuring a safe and secure fit. The crib skirt gives the finishing touch to your child’s crib. It is a gray and white chevron print on the top and a textured gray fabric on the bottom with gray tassel trim in between the two fabrics. Complete this incredible jungle nursery with these custom jumbo wall decals featuring our tall giraffe, elephant, sloth, branches and leaves. They add a designer touch to a feature wall in the baby’s room.

name: Diapers Pack - up & up - (Select Size and Count)
description: Our up & up™ diapers feature SuperAbsorb™ Channels that absorb quickly to help keep your baby dry while offering day or night leak protection. Feel at ease knowing up & up™ diapers have a gentle-touch dryness liner that is clinically proven gentle and hypoallergenic. With soft and stretchy waist and sides, and a breathable outer cover, these premium absorbency diapers will provide dryness and comfort for your baby.WARNING: to avoid danger of suffocation, keep this and any plastic bags away from children and pets. To avoid risk, do not allow your child to play with diaper packaging. Choking can result from anything children put in their mouths. Discard any torn or unsealed diaper. Do not use diaper as a pillow.CAUTION: Like most clothing, diaper will burn if exposed to flame. Always keep your child away from any source of flame. PLEASE: Before disposing, shake soil into toilet wrap diaper tightly and discard in waste receptacle. DO NOT FLUSH. PLEASE DO NOT LITTER. IF you notice a small amount of gel-like material on your child’s skin, don’t be alarmed. This comes from the padding and can be easily wiped away. Diapers should not be worn in swimming pools as they will absorb water and become very heavy.

name: NoJo Mama's Little Llama Crib Set - 4pc
description: Mama's Little Llama 4 Piece Crib Bedding Set includes a comforter, 100% cotton crib sheet, dust ruffle and nursery organizer. The comforter features mama with her baby's grazing along the mountainside in soft shades of gray, white, charcoal and beige. The comforter measures 36" x 45". The fitted cotton crib sheet is a playful allover llama print in shades of gray and white and measures 28" x 52" with elastic edges for a snug fit. The matching dust ruffle is a solid gray detailed with ric rac trim. Keep your nursery tidy with the handy organizer that measures 12" x 8" x 6" and comes in a gray stripe pattern with allover llama print on the inside. This gender-neutral group is perfect for any nursery. NoJo only the best for baby!

name: Lambs & Ivy Big Sky Blue/Brown Woodland Animals 4-Piece Baby Crib Bedding Set
description: This four-piece nursery crib bedding set includes one quilt, one fitted crib sheet, one crib skirt (dust ruffle), and a complete set of wall decals. Your little adventurer will love this amazing woodland forest wildlife bedding collection. The quilt features an appliqued chocolate brown velour moose, a rusty brown velour bison and a brown minky bear with two creamy tan velour baby bears. They are under a moonlit, starry sky surrounded by majestic mountains and natural rivers. The breathable 100% cotton fitted crib sheet is on a white ground and features mommy and baby bears, moose, bison, mountains, rivers, trees, and plants. There is elastic all the way around ensuring a safe and secure fit on a standard sized crib mattress measuring 28” X 52”. The 4-sided crib skirt is in a cotton rich navy twill. The lower panel is 100% cotton chambray. On the right corner there are appliqued mountains along with a chambray color blue moon. It has a 14 ½” drop. The complete set of wall decals include four sheets and feature 13 die-cut pieces. Included is a 16” (diagonal length) moose, one 13” tall brown mommy bear with a sand color baby bear on her back. An 8” tall baby bear is close by. Colorful mountains, pine trees, a winding river, two additional trees and a gray moon complete this mural like wall decal. They are easy to apply and work best on smooth walls.

name: Lambs & Ivy Star Wars Signature Millennium Falcon 4-Piece Baby Crib Bedding Set
description: Your little padawan (Jedi-in-training) will love how their nursery is transformed into a Star Wars Millennium Falcon adventure from a galaxy far far away. The four-piece nursery crib bedding set includes one quilt, one breathable 100% cotton fitted crib sheet, one crib skirt and a set of Star Wars logo wall decals. The quilt features a 17” tall Chewbacca made in a high pile fur texture brown minky fabric complete with his bandolier which is embroidered in black and white. C-3PO is next to him, is 11” in height and is appliqued in a yellow fuzzy soft minky fabric with gold metallic embroidery stitches. Our favorite droid, R2D2, is 8 ½” tall and is appliqued with white cotton twill, silver knit and dark blue embroidery stitches. An amazing interior view of the iconic holochess scene of Chewbacca and C-3PO playing Dejarik in the Millennium Falcon is featured on this amazing quilt. The 31” wide couch is behind the holochess table, which features metallic fabric details, and is trimmed with gray cording. Outside the Millennium Falcon is the misty blue galaxy print filled with planets, star dust, X-Wings, Tie Fighters, and a metallic Death Star. The quilt also has a shell stitch embroidery detail. The back of the quilt is the dusty blue galaxy in a cotton rich twill. The breathable 100% cotton fitted crib sheet is a tossed print with Chewbacca, C-3PO, R2D2 and the Millennium Falcon. It is on a gray ground and has elastic all the way around ensuring a safe and secure fit on a standard size crib mattress measuring 52” x 28”. The blue galaxy print crib skirt has a 16” drop, shell stitch embroidery, and the appliqued Millennium Falcon with embroidered stitching is on the right corner panel. Star Wars logo wall decals are included in this bedding set and has four sheets that are 12” X 18” each making an approximate 42" x 32" design when complete. There are 17 pre-cut pieces. The words Star Wars are printed in blue with dark gray outlines. C-3PO is in yellow gold, Chewbacca (7" x 9.75") stands on the letter A (8" x 7") with his fists up in the air, Darth Vader patrols the letter W complete with his lightsaber, Yoda (4" x 4.25") stands close by and R2D2, an Ewok, and some 2.25" blue stars complete this Star Wars Decal. They are easy to apply and will not harm your walls.

name: Trend Lab Crib Bedding Set - Save the Polar Bears - 4pc
description: Make your baby the coolest kid in the crib with the Trend Lab 4 Piece 100% Cotton Save the Polar Bears Crib Bedding Collection by Trend Lab. This 4-piece crib bedding set features simple narwhals, whales, polar bears, and penguins smiling sweetly on a fresh blue background. The nursery quilt is 100% Cotton and fully reversible featuring a print of the arctic animals on one side, with a modern blue and white print on the back. The set includes two 100% cotton fitted crib sheets that feature a print of the arctic animals and a simple modern pattern in a clean blue and white palette. Finish the look of your crib with a coordinating crib skirt in 100% cotton to tie your nursery together in a perfectly modern style. This product is STANDARD 100 by OEKO-TEX certified, meaning it is free from harmful levels of chemical substances. Please adhere to JPMA’s Safe Infant Bedding Practices.Oeko-Tex certified.

name: Lambs & Ivy Disney Baby Magical Mickey Mouse 3-Piece Crib Bedding Set - Gray
description: Transform your nursery into the Magical World of Disney with this spectacular baby bedding collection called Magical Mickey Mouse. The 3-piece set includes one quilt, one 100% cotton fitted crib sheet and one crib skirt. Classic Mickey Mouse loves wearing his favorite red shorts, white gloves and shoes. He is expertly appliqued and embroidered on a heather gray cotton ground. Elaborated bean stitching is featured along with embroidered stars and included is Mickey’s famous black ears. The 100% cotton fitted crib sheet is on a white ground with Mickey in various positions. The fitted sheet has elastic all around providing a safe and secure fit. The crib skirt gives the finishing touch to your child’s crib. It is a gray twill bordered with a darker gray twill on the bottom and separated by a white cotton flange. The front lower right corner is appliqued with the word MICKEY along with his famous black ears.

The fourth piece in this set is a Snuggle Sleeper™ (aka wearable blanket) in a soft 100% cotton interlock fabric with an adorable elephant applique. It is size small. Imported.

name: Bedtime Originals Astronaut Snoopy 5-Piece Navy/Blue Space Toddler Bedding Set
description: The perfect way for your little one to transition from their crib is into a toddler bed. They share the same size mattress making switching a snap. Your little explorer will love this out of this world toddler bedding set. It features Snoopy standing on a gray moon next to his navy spaceship. Astronaut Snoopy is wearing his orange spacesuit, his helmet, and red scarf. Of course, Astronaut Woodstock, wearing his space helmet, is right by his side. There is a Neptune Blue background with yellow and silver stars and an orange Saturn floating in the distance. Trimmed with a gray inner border, a navy outer border and separated by an orange flange. The top and bottom sheets feature Snoopy in various poses floating among the stars and planets on the navy background. The fitted bottom sheet has elastic all the way around ensuring a snug fit. The top sheet is 44” X 60” and the bottom fitted sheet is 28” X 52”. The standard size pillowcase is 20” X 31 ½”. It features Snoopy in space with a gray and blue satellite floating overhead. This toddler bed set is made from a soft microfiber fabric. It is machine washable and very durable for easy care. The set of decals with Snoopy, Woodstock, and his spaceship complete a fun space theme for your child’s room. There are 21 die-cut pieces. Each letter in the name Snoopy is 5 ½” tall. There are 12 stars that are approximately 1 ½” in width. These are easy to apply and will not harm your walls. Imported

If you're looking for a cute and neutral baby shower gift, baby registry addition, or upgrade for your own baby's outfits - this is the perfect baby accessory.

name: Lambs & Ivy Hall of Fame Sports Animals 5-Piece Crib Bedding Set - Gray/Blue
description: Welcome your little athlete home with this sport-inspired baby bedding collection. The nursery crib bedding set comes complete with one quilt (36” X 45”), one 100% cotton fitted crib sheet, one 4-sided crib skirt, one plush minky football, and a complete set of wall decals. This asymmetrical patchwork quilt has six unique fabric panels. Featured sports are baseball, basketball, football, and soccer. The textured appliqued and embroidered animals are all playing their favorite sports. The lion is playing soccer and holding a trophy, the zebra is playing football, the elephant is playing baseball, and the giraffe is playing basketball. The breathable 100% cotton fitted crib sheet is a tossed print and includes elephants, zebras, lions, and giraffes at play along with trophies and verbiage sayings of “slam dunk” and “the catch.” The fitted crib sheet is designed to fit a standard crib mattress measuring 52” X 28”. The crib skirt is a crosshatch print in gray and white. The border is navy and is separated from the gray crosshatch with a white twill flange. There are two pleats on the front panel and the crib skirt has a 14 ½” drop. Included in the bedding set is a complete set of easy on, easy off wall decals that make up nine triangular pennants in gray, navy, blue, and tan along with six stars. The decals are a great way to make a feature wall in the nursery and they won’t harm your walls. This crib bedding set is a top baby registry pick and is a wow gift at any baby shower!

name: Charlie Banana Reusable Swim Diaper with Snaps - (Select Size & Pattern)
description: At Charlie Banana, we care for your baby and our planet at the same time. Our reusable and washable swim diapers with snaps on both sides feature our signature softness, a snug fit, and lightweight waterproof materials that protect your baby's delicate skin without swelling in the water. We use only safe materials, rigorously tested for harmful substances, and certified under STANDARD 100 by OEKO-TEX®. Additionally, our super soft inner lining is made from plant-based TENCEL® Lyocell fibers, so that only the softest materials touch your little one's skin.In the box, you'll find one reusable and washable swim diaper with waist snaps, a waterproof outer lining, and a soft TENCEL® lyocell inner lining. Our swim diapers come in four sizes (small, medium, large, and X-large), so you can select the perfect size for your baby. Simply:1. Use the diaper,2. Rinse it,3. Toss it in the wash,4. Reuse again and again!There are multiple benefits of Charlie Banana reusable and washable swim diapers:• Side-snaps for easy-on and easy-off. Even when wet or dirty, our swim diapers with side-snaps work together with the wide elastic back, and leg elastics to contain solids and prevent leaks, as well as making changes quick and easy. All the fun and comfort, without the mess!• Lightweight comfort with no swelling. With waterproof, breathable, and quick-drying fabric, our swim diaper provides lightweight comfort that doesn't swell when wet, so your baby can move freely in the water.• Long-lasting and fun prints. Made from long-lasting, high-quality materials; they also come in cute prints just like a swimsuit, with colors that last, even after multiple washes.Charlie Banana products are made with your baby’s world in mind. When caring for our planet, we don’t just talk the talk; we walk the walk by donating 1% of our sales to support environmental and conservation causes.

name: Bedtime Originals Lavender Floral 3-Piece Baby Crib Bedding Set - Pink/Purple
description: Dress your baby’s crib with this stunning watercolor floral three-piece infant nursery crib bedding set. Included is one quilt/comforter, one floral fitted crib sheet and one crib skirt made in a soft microfiber material. This lovely floral design has pretty shades of pinks and lavenders with a touch of sunshine yellow. Our favorite roses and peonies flowers decorate the quilt along with graceful flowy leaves. The fitted crib sheet has elastic all the way around ensuring a safe and secure fit on a standard-size crib mattress measuring 28” X 52”. The crib skirt adds the finishing touch and is a beautiful shade of lavender purple. It is shirred for a more luxurious look and has a 10” drop.

name: The Peanutshell Aflutter Baby Crib Bedding Set, Pink Floral/Butterfly - 3pc
description: The beauty of nature comes to life in this 3-piece floral baby crib bedding set featuring the Aflutter collection by The Peanutshell. In the quilt, shades of pink and aqua play against a white ground with shimmery gold metallic accents, with flowers and butterflies tossed together on a brushstroke background, all printed on soft, easy-care microfiber. name: Bedtime Originals Winnie The Pooh Hugs Crib Bedding Set - 3pc
description: Winnie the Pooh is one of Disney’s most loved characters. This enchanting three-piece crib bedding set features a 17 ½” appliqued and embroidered Winnie the Pooh. He is standing on a light heather gray background with his hands shyly covering his belly button and a sweet smile on his face. His shirt is made of a soft mint color velour. Tigger is in the upper corner patch hugging his favorite baby blue star. Little Piglet is close by too and is sitting on a fluffy cloud surrounded by colorful stars. The words “You are so Loved” are neatly placed in the center-left patch among these three happy characters. There is a 3” border around the quilt. This collection is made in a soft microfiber fabrication. The fitted crib sheet features Pooh in several different positions, Tigger hugging yellow and blue stars, and Piglet sitting on a cloud looking at the sky filled with stars, clouds, and the moon. The fitted crib sheet has elastic all the way around ensuring a safe and secure fit on a standard size crib mattress measuring 52” X 28”. The top panel of the coordinating crib skirt is a soft minty color, has a one-inch white stripe below and the bottom is a solid maize color. The crib skirt is 10” long and adds the finishing touch to this charming collection.

name: Disney Lion King Nursery Crib Bedding Set - 6pc

name: Lambs & Ivy Floral Garden Watercolor/Pink Linen 5-Piece Baby Crib Bedding Set
description: The 5-piece nursery baby crib bedding set includes one quilt, one breathable 100% cotton fitted crib sheet, one shirred crib skirt/dust ruffle, one decorative pillow and one complete set of large flower wall decals. A beautiful shade of pink was selected for this bedding set. The quilt is fully reversible. One side is a gorgeous linen blend fabric with 30 pin tucks along with a beautiful long pink ruffle with a baby hemmed edge. The other side of the quilt is 100% cotton and is a beautiful large watercolor floral print. The breathable 100% cotton crib sheet is a stunning watercolor floral print featuring oversized flowers. This placement sheet makes a great photo opportunity for sharing with family and on social media. The pretty pink linen blend crib skirt is shirred all around and has split corners for easy placement around the posts. It is finished with a baby hem and is 14 ½” long. An expertly stitched pink pin-tucked linen blend pillow is included with this bedding set. Sized at 19” X 13” with a 2” soft ruffle. Complete this upscale nursery bedding set with a complete set of wall decals. They feature blossoming flowers in various sizes in shades of pink with touches of black and white and dark green leaves. The Floral Garden crib bedding set is a top baby registry item and makes an amazing baby shower gift. Please note: set includes one set of wall decals which contains 8 flowers and leaves; nursery photo is shown with 2 sets of wall decals as additional sets are available separately.

name: Lambs & Ivy Jungle Safari Gray/Tan/White Nursery 6-Piece Baby Crib Bedding Set
description: This six-piece crib bedding set includes one quilt, two cotton fitted crib sheets, one crib skirt, one wearable blanket (recommended for safe sleep), and a set of wall decals to complete your nursery decor. The neutral color palette makes it perfect for boys or girls. Babies, infants, and kids will love the safari animals including a lion, giraffe, elephant, and zebra. Dimensional trims along with soft furry fabrics and embroidered details add to this popular themed baby bedding set. The back of the quilt is 100% cotton. The 100% cotton, breathable fitted crib sheets include one tossed animal print and one solid gray. A dotted print with gray furry trim completes the decorative crib skirt. Included for safe sleep is a 100% cotton interlock wearable blanket with lion applique. Fits a size small - medium. Add a designer touch with these easy on easy off wall decals. Included is a happy giraffe, a sweet elephant, a courageous lion, and a colorful tree. Finish your jungle safari nursery theme with additional accessories sold separately, such as an extra fitted sheet, baby blanket, plush elephant stuffed animal - Jett, musical baby crib mobile, and additional wall decals.

name: Lambs & Ivy Woodland Forest Animal Nursery 5-Piece Baby Crib Bedding Set - Gray
description: This Woodland Forest 5-piece nursery baby crib bedding set includes one highly detailed quilt, two 100% cotton fitted crib sheets, one crib skirt (dust ruffle) and a full set of wall decals/appliques. This woodland designed quilt features a friendly gray corduroy bear with diamond shaped embroideries and a cute little walnut colored squirrel marching happily on his back. A tan colored mischievous minky fox sits close by and has a 3 dimensional tail with embroidered details. All the while a wise owl with dimensional herringbone wings stands proudly on an appliqued branch with embroidered leaves. The back of the quilt is an on trend gray herringbone print. One of the 100% cotton fitted crib sheets is a trendy two-toned chevron print and the other 100% cotton fitted crib sheet is an adorable animal print with our favorite woodland critters. The crib skirt is in a warm gray, has two pleats, the bottom is a walnut colored arrow print and a white twill tape separates the two fabrics. Complete this whimsical woodland theme with our easy on easy off wall decals. The tree branches and leaves come in separate pieces so you can arrange the leaves any way you wish. Included are Oscar, our friendly bear along with the wise owl, mischievous fox and spunky squirrel.

name: Weleda Comforting Bath Cream - 6.8 fl oz
description: Wash baby’s skin with this extra-mild Weleda Comforting Cream Bath for delicate skin. Calendula’s sunny warmth and skin soothing powers are matched with silky sweet almond oil and sesame oil to prevent drying, in a truly nourishing blend. Warm and pampering on the skin, kindly cleansing, it’s a bath made to keep skin soft, smooth and with the lovely fragrance of clean baby.Key Ingredients:• CALENDULA FLOWER EXTRACT: This gentle and nourishing botanical possesses soothing properties. Commonly referred to as Marigold, this annual herb is from the Family Asteraceae, the Sunflower Family. The Calendula plant is comprised of carotenoids, flavonoids and essential oils.• SWEET ALMOND OIL: The fine and light sweet almond oil is very skin-friendly and ideal for sensitive, dry skin. Sweet almond oil is very suitable for the care of infants and small children. It is characterized by a high content of unsaturated fatty oils, such as oil and linolenic acid.How to Use: Shake the bottle and add 2-3 splashes to a warm bath when the water has been run. Mix in gently by hand.Packaging contains recycled content – 97% rPET in each bottle. Help Weleda stay green! Weleda and TerraCycle have partnered together to create a free recycling program for all Weleda packaging. Click here to join in: https://www.terracycle.com/en-US/brigades/weleda. Weleda's personal care products are certified natural by the European organization NATRUE. In accordance with NATRUE standards, Weleda does not conduct any animal testing, and is committed to maintaining high ethical standards for its personal care products.

name: Lambs & Ivy Baby Noah 3-Piece Animals/Ark Baby Crib Bedding Set - Blue/Brown
description: All afloat on Noah’s boat. This three-piece nursery crib bedding set includes one quilt, one breathable 100% cotton fitted crib sheet, and one crib skirt (dust ruffle). Upscale fabrications of minky, boucle, sherpa, velour, woven fabrics and knits were used to create this amazing baby bedding set. Eddie the elephant is appliqued in taupe velour and has a cute furry textured sherpa sheep standing on his back. Leonardo, the lion, is appliqued in a textured woven fabric and has a 3-dimensional fringe mane. There are stacked animals on the left side of the quilt that include a tall giraffe made of curly boucle, a friendly bear, and a silly alligator standing with one foot on top of the bear’s head. A white velour dove and a white sherpa sheep add to the fun. In the distance is Noah’s Ark made in a thermal knit along with majestic mountains. The breathable 100% cotton fitted crib sheet features giraffes, bears, rhinos, lions, elephants, sheep, alligators, whales , rabbits, and doves. name: Kolcraft 2-Stage Antibacterial Baby Crib Mattress and Toddler Bed Mattress
description: Family owned and operated since 1946, Kolcraft takes pride in leading the crib mattress industry with safe, high-quality and value-friendly baby mattresses. Every baby deserves a safe sleeping environment, which is why every crib mattress we make uses materials screened for air quality, chemicals and lasting durability. Kolcraft helped to craft quality standards that today helps to help ensure every baby mattress on the market would be made with better safety. Kolcraft makes every baby crib mattress and toddler mattress in our own factory for hands-on quality control of each component. Our American-made steel coils are heat-tempered for longevity and our American made cushioning and comfort materials pass durability testing above and beyond any standard. Our baby crib mattresses are made by experts in the industry and tested by independent laboratories for ASTM crib mattress safety standards, GREENGUARD GOLD Air Quality Certification and Chemicals of High Concern to Children regulations. Our baby mattresses also pass all CPSIA standards, extra durability and firmness tests, crib fit tests for safety and many more.The Kolcraft Nursery Collection of lively patterns feature Starry Night Stars and Moons, Woodland Forest Animal Friends, Jungle Safari Animal Friends with natural colors for baby girl and baby boy nursery decor. The Kolcraft baby crib mattress is a 2-stage dual firm innerspring crib mattress upgraded with an EPA-registered antibacterial surface that is gentle on baby and has been lab-tested to show a reduction in the spread of bacteria. The airy innerspring line of crib mattresses use extra firm steel coils, airy yet firm cushioning. The 2-Stage baby mattress and toddler mattress offers a slightly firmer side for infants and a cozier toddler side for grow-with-me quality feel. The crib mattress cover is waterproof, repels odors and wipes clean with a damp cloth. Engineered with high quality steel coils interwoven for extra firmness and lasting durability. Coils flex under baby's body weight while the airy cushioning supports growing infants and toddlers without excess pressure on fragile bones. The waterproof cover is designed with an airflow pocket to help the mattress breathe. Our supportive cushioning is sustainably sourced locally in the US. Non-toxic no imported foams or toxic fire retardants. Fits snugly in USA standard size cribs and toddler beds. Ultra-lightweight coil mattress weighs only 10 pounds to easily flip and change crib sheets. Measures about 52"L x 27.5"W x 5" thick. 10 year warranty for workmanship and materials. Parents have depended on Kolcraft for American-made quality baby products for over 77 years!

name: Johnson's Baby Shampoo - 13.6 fl oz
description: Johnson's Baby Shampoo provides a mild, gentle clean that won't irritate your baby's eyes during bath time. Specially formulated for fine baby hair and delicate scalp, this gentle cleansing baby hair shampoo gently washes away dirt and germs as it leaves your little one's hair soft, shiny, clean and smelling baby fresh. The Johnson's No More Tears formula is as gentle to the eyes as pure water and won't irritate baby's eyes during bath time. This tear-free baby shampoo is hypoallergenic, pediatrician-tested, and free of parabens, phthalates, sulfates, and dyes. To use, wet baby's hair with warm water, apply tear-free baby shampoo, gently lather, and rinse. For over 125 years, Johnson's formulas have been specially designed for baby's unique and delicate skin and hair. We collaborated with and listened to 11,500 parents, midwives, and pediatricians around the world.

name: Chicco Glow in The Dark Sippy Cup 12M+ - Pink 9oz
description: Keep baby's beverage cool and easy to find with the Chicco Glow In The Dark Insulated Rim Spout Trainer Sippy Cup. The double-wall design keeps drinks cooler longer and prevents sweating, and the narrow-edge spout is designed to train toddlers to drink from the rim of a cup. With a unique ergonomic design, this bite-proof spout encourages proper lower lip positioning with plenty of space for little noses. Spills have never been easier to avoid. With the one-piece construction silicone valve in place, gentle sipping activates the flow of liquid from the spout. You can flip the sippy cup upside down and all around without leaking a drop. Or easily remove the valve for practice with free-flow drinking. The contoured shape of the cup is specially designed for tiny hands to grab and hold. The Chicco Glow In The Dark Insulated Rim-Spout Trainer Sippy is loved by kids and parents alike with adorable illustrations decorating each cup and mix and match lids for the perfect color combo. For a quick and easy wash, all parts are dishwasher safe. With minimal parts that are all interchangeable, the Chicco Glow In The Dark Insulated Rim Spout Trainer Sippy Cup is exactly what every parent needs: functional, minimalistic, easy to clean, and loved by big and little kids alike.

name: Lambs & Ivy Jungle Friends 5-Piece Safari Animals Nursery Baby Crib Bedding Set
description: This 5-piece nursery crib baby bedding set includes one quilt, one breathable 100% cotton fitted crib sheet, one crib skirt (dust ruffle), one lovey (security blanket) and a complete set of wall decals. Surrounded by colorful leaves, these friendly animals are oh so soft and cuddly. Our furry giraffe stands 27” tall and is fully appliqued in an apricot luxury high pile fur. His spots are a soft minky and he has a fringe mane. His face is expertly embroidered. The playful lion is a soft honey color with a furry fringe mane and is ready to roar. Our majestic gray elephant stands 14” tall. He has large floppy 3-D velveteen ears and a silver-gray fringe tail. His face and tusk are embroidered. The back of the quilt is a pistachio green leaf print. The breathable 100% cotton fitted crib sheet includes all of our friendly jungle animals along with trees, leaves and birds. It has elastic all the way around ensuring a safe and secure fit on a standard size crib mattress measuring 52” X 28”. The crib skirt adds the finishing touch to your child’s crib. The upper panel is a cotton rich blend with green leaves and the lower panel is a linen viscose blend and it has a 14 ½” drop. Included in this set is a 14” X 14” elephant lovey (security blanket) made of a soft luxury coral fleece. The elephant is made of soft gray velour. Wall Decals are included in this bedding set as well. They are a great way to add a feature wall to the nursery and create a mural like look. Included are one giraffe, one elephant, one lion, a bird, frog, and multiple sized leaves. There are four sheets that are 12” X 18” each. They are pre-cut, easy to apply and will not harm your walls upon removal. There are 12 complete shapes, made of 13 total stickers.

name: Lambs & Ivy Sky Rocket 5-Piece Blue Galaxy/Space Nursery Baby Crib Bedding Set
description: Your little one will love exploring the moon, planets, and stars with this out of the world nursery crib baby bedding collection. These decals are easy to apply to smooth walls and will not harm your walls upon removal.

name: Tommee Tippee Insulated 9oz Spill Proof Portable Toddler Straw Cup - Orange
description: Being a toddler is thirsty work, so it’s important to keep them hydrated and encourage them to drink more water. Specially designed for little ones who are busy walking, running and climbing, the Tommee Tippee Insulated Non-Spill Straw Cup is perfectly sized for small hands and can hold 9oz of cold liquid. Together with a fun-to-flip straw, staying hydrated has never been this much fun. Equipped with innovative anti-leak technology, the bottle is completely leak-proof even when turned upside down or shaken. Our unique valve seals and regulates the flow of liquid to stop leaks and to ensure easy drinking. Suitable for toddlers aged 12 months and beyond, the Non-Spill Straw cup has a flip opening that’s simple to use. Toddlers will love drinking from their bright and colorful cups to stay hydrated throughout the day. For added protection against bite marks, the durable, long lasting one-piece spout is gentle on little mouths but tough enough to withstand tiny teeth. They are handsomely packaged, machine-washable for easy care, and they fit small or medium infants weighing 7-14 lbs. Their adjustable design ensures a snug, reassuring fit while allowing growing room for your baby to make the most of the swaddling experience. Nurture your infant's feelings of safety and trust. name: Re-Play Spill Proof Cup - 10oz
description: Re-Play's No-Spill Sippy Cups are ideal for everyday dining. Perfect for backyard parties, picnics, camping, barbecues, etc. You will find yourself using them as the go to on-the-go children's cups! The one-piece, easy clean silicone valve keeps your toddler's milk or juice leak-free. Durable AND affordable, our sippy cups are perfect for everyday use - as well as outdoor parties, picnics, and barbecues. Mix and match these colorful cups with our utensils, plates, and bowls, to create a vibrant tableware set! While our products are microwave safe, we only recommend putting them in for short 20 second bursts, in order to warm the food, NOT COOK. Extended time in the microwave can cause uneven heating and hotpots in the food. Do not put Re-Play in a regular oven. Re-Play products are dishwasher safe - because every mom and dad deserve less clean-up time! When serving red sauces, we recommend immediately scrubbing and rinsing, using a grease-cutting, liquid soap before dishwashing. Our family owned and operated company uses SUSTAINABLE, Recycled HDPE (Milk Jugs) in our manufacturing process. Re-Play saves 1 milk jug from the landfill every 6 seconds, completely reducing single use plastic.

name: Charlie Banana Reusable Swim Diaper with Adjustable Drawstring - (Select Size & Pattern)
description: At Charlie Banana, we care for your baby and our planet at the same time. Our reusable and washable swim diapers with adjustable drawstring feature our signature softness, a snug fit, and lightweight waterproof materials that protect your baby's delicate skin without swelling in the water. We use only safe materials, rigorously tested for harmful substances, and certified under STANDARD 100 by OEKO-TEX®. Additionally, our super soft inner lining is made from plant-based TENCEL® Lyocell fibers, so that only the softest materials touch your little one's skin.In the box, you'll find one reusable and washable swim diaper with adjustable drawstring, a waterproof outer lining, and a soft TENCEL® lyocell inner lining. Our swim diapers come in four sizes (small, medium, large, and X-large), so you can select the perfect size for your baby. Simply:1. Pull the diaper up, adjust the drawstring and let the fun begin!2. Rinse it afterwards,3. Toss it in the wash,4. Reuse again and again!There are multiple benefits of Charlie Banana reusable and washable swim diapers:• Adjustable fit to prevent leaks. The adjustable waist drawstring and leg elastics allow for a custom, snug, and comfy fit that helps prevent leaks. You can easily pull them on and off like swimwear--ideal for wriggly or potty trained babies.• Lightweight comfort with no swelling. With waterproof, breathable, and quick-drying fabric, our swim diaper provides lightweight comfort that doesn't swell when wet, so your baby can move freely in the water.• Long-lasting and fun prints. Made from long-lasting, high-quality materials; they also come in cute prints just like a swimsuit, with colors that last, even after multiple washes.Charlie Banana products are made with your baby’s world in mind. When caring for our planet, we don’t just talk the talk; we walk the walk by donating 1% of our sales to support environmental and conservation causes.

For the daily maintenance of eczema-prone skin, use Eucerin Baby Eczema Cream after bathing.

name: Lambs & Ivy Baby Farm Animals 5-Piece White/Taupe Baby Crib Bedding Set
description: The Baby Farm 5-piece nursery baby bedding crib set includes a crib quilt, 2 fitted crib sheets, crib skirt, and a full set of wall decals. This classic Baby Farm patchwork quilt includes two appliqued furry sheep, a black and white cow made in soft velour with appliqued details, a taupe color suede horse with a black velour mane, white clouds, two gray minky birds, and two appliqued trees. When your child is ready to begin his potty training journey, the Pull-Ups brand can help. Visit the Pull-Ups website for expert articles, tips and potty training resources. We've helped potty train 60 million Big Kids and counting!** Pull-Ups New Leaf Training Pants are available in sizes 2T-3T (16-34 lbs), 3T-4T (32-40 lbs) and 4T-5T (38-50 lbs). name: Sealy FlexCool 2-Stage Crib And Toddler Mattress
description: Give baby an extra firm sleeping foundation plus airy cushioning with the Sealy FlexCool 2-Stage Crib and Toddler Mattress. This dual sided mattress features a firmer side for infants, as recommended by doctors, and a softer side for toddlers to accommodate growing babies. A 204 heavy gauge innerspring steel core provides premium firmness for baby, plus weight distribution bars help prevent sagging and keep infants well supported. For added protection, a full perimeter border wire plus EverEdge pylons keeps the sides, corners and edges of the mattress firm. The toddler side of the mattress features a light and airy cushioning layer that flexes under baby’s weight for contoured support. Hypoallergenic sleeping layers plus a cotton wrap add additional durability and comfort. A PVC-free fabric cover is soft and breathable on baby’s skin and offers a waterproof barrier for moisture protection and easy cleaning. This mattress passes safety, quality and chemical testing to ensure baby is safe and sound on a Sealy, plus the entire mattress is GREENGUARD Gold Certified for low chemical emissions to help create a healthier nursery for baby.

name: Colgate Mattress Little Aristocrat Crib Mattress
description: The Little Aristocrat by Colgate Mattress® is a top-quality, 6″ innerspring crib mattress, made of 70 coils of thick 13.5-gauge tempered steel and 9.0-gauge border rods. This spring unit offers sturdy edge support and increased firmness for baby’s safety and proper development. A sustainable insulator pad made of bonded felt and two comfortable and supportive cushioning layers surround the spring unit. Increased internal air flow and freshness is assured by multiple side vents, and mattress durability is provided by strong cloth binding. These high quality materials are protected by a triple-layered reinforced, waterproof, and tear-resistant mattress cover that is easy to clean with damp cloth and mild soap. Like all Colgate mattresses, the Colgate Little Aristocrat is GREENGUARD ® Gold certified, CertiPUR-US ® certified, CPSIA certified, and compliant with all federal and state flammability requirements – without the use of fire retardant chemicals. The Little Aristocrat is proudly handcrafted by Colgate, the Crib Mattress Specialist ®, a family-owned and operated business dedicated to baby’s safety since 1955.

name: Organic Dream Comfort Supreme 2-Stage Crib & Toddler Mattress
description: The ComfortSupreme 2-Stage Crib Mattress represents a new evolution in safe sleep for infants and toddlers. It is the only baby mattress that is 100% Washable and 100% Breathable with 100% Organic Cotton. Designed using only the cleanest and purest materials for babies, the ComfortSupreme maximizes your baby’s health and safety from Day 1. Designed with a patented SUPREME Organic Cover, this mattress is extra comfortable for your little one and naturally hypoallergenic to nurture their skin and body. The DREAMCORE is 100% Washable and promotes excellent airflow throughout the entire core of the mattress, allowing air to flow channel from the core up to the surface. Nothing is more important than keeping your baby safe, and Organic Dream is committed to helping you keep your baby safe. Our crib mattresses for babies are made from certified organic cotton and other premium materials from sources you can feel good about. We are proudly GREENGUARD Gold Certified, the highest industry safety standard ensuring the lowest VOCs and chemical emissions. Our breathable crib mattress is proven to significantly reduce the risk of suffocation in babies and toddlers, thanks to the breathable layers that ensure ongoing airflow all through the night and during every nap, even for face and belly sleepers. The hypoallergenic materials are perfect on sensitive skin, which all babies have. Your baby will love cuddling up on this super-snuggly baby mattress. Not only are our baby crib mattresses top of the line for their safety measures and standards, but they also provide comfort and support for your little one. We offer a variety of mattress options to best suit your family's needs. name: Mustela Stelatopia Skin Soothing Baby Pajamas for Eczema Prone Skin - (Select Size Group)
description: Mustela Stelatopia Skin Soothing Pajamas are designed for babies and toddlers with eczema. Using microcapsule technology, these 100% cotton pajamas deliver skin soothing moisture to the skin throughout the night. Each microcapsule contains 5 natural ingredients: Avocado Oil, Sunflower Oil Distillate, Squalane, Ceramides and Vitamin E. Avocado Oil works to maintain the skin's moisture barrier while Sunflower Oil Distillate, known for its soothing properties, replenishes the skin with much needed lipids. These ingredients are activated when they come in contact with the skin and help to keep it soothed, comfortable and moisturized all night long. This new generation of sleepwear is clinically proven to improve baby 's sleep. Babies fall asleep 2X quicker* and wake up 2X less throughout the night*. Designed with growing baby in mind, pajamas feature adjustable snap closures. Made with OEKO-TEK certified cotton, which is free of any allergens or potentially harmful substances. Dermatologist and Pediatrician tested and endorsed by the National Eczema Association. *Consumer study in partnership with the French Eczema Association, results after 3 weeks in 14 children.

name: Changing Pad Portable for Baby and Toddler by Comfy Cubs
description: A Clean Baby is a Happy and Healthy Baby Parents are busy, especially when you’re trying to balance your work and home life, do some shopping, keep your baby close, and handle all your responsibilities. That means you don’t always have time to lug around a big, bulky changing table or wipe down everything in the public bathroom, just so you can change your baby. That’s why we developed the Comfy Cubs Baby Changing Pad that lets you quickly and easily lay your baby down, get them cleaned up, and stay on the go with little mess and far less stress. name: Vaseline Baby Hypoallergenic Petroleum Healing Jelly & Diaper Rash Skin Protectant - 13oz
description: A baby's skin is very sensitive, so the discomfort of diaper rash is never pleasant for either of you. A daily application of Vaseline Petroleum Jelly Baby keeps your baby’s skin soft and smooth and adds a protective barrier that helps prevent friction between the diaper and your baby’s skin. And that can help prevent diaper rash before it even occursLike the original Vaseline Jelly formulated back in 1870, our Vaseline Petroleum Jelly Baby is triple purified to remove any impurities that could irritate your child’s skin and heals dry skin without leaving behind a greasy residue. This protective Vaseline Jelly locks in moisture to help the skin's natural moisture barrier recover from daily exposure to environmental triggers that break down the natural barrier like diapers for instanceVaseline Petroleum Jelly Baby is gentle, dermatologist tested, and formulated to soothe diaper rash and yet is gentle enough to be used on your baby’s sensitive skin. Our pure and gentle formula means Vaseline Petroleum Jelly Baby can be used as a daily baby moisturizer to treat dry patches on your baby’s face and body, and not just around their diaper area. When used regularly as part of your diaper changing routine, Vaseline Petroleum Jelly Baby is the perfect baby moisturizer to help prevent dry skin and chafing from diaper rashWe’re working with Direct Relief in our mission to promote better skin health around the world. The Healing Project provides dermatological care, Vaseline Jelly and medical supplies needed to help heal the skin of people affected by poverty or emergencies around the world

description: Bubbles for All A great childhood is made of many small joys, and for some lucky kids, bubble baths are included. We believe that no child deserves to be itchy, irritated, or infected, especially not as a result of using a bath product. Your toddler bubble bath pods are backed by our commitment to your complete satisfaction. Raise kids who love to bathe, with TruKid.

name: The Honest Company Babe's Clean Bum All-In-One Gift Set - 4pk
description: Babe's first mess? Don't stress! These starter essentials help make diaper changing a breeze by soothing + cleaning your babe's bum. They're all fragrance free, making them perfect for lil' one's sensitive skin. And if a changing disaster does happen (don't worry, we get it), our baby laundry detergent has your back! Perfect for cleaning any oopsies. This clean-up starter set is perfect for an upcoming baby shower + expecting mama!Made Without:Plant-Based Baby Wipes made without alcohol, parabens, chlorine processing, and fragrancesSoothing Bottom Wash made without SLS, PEGs, phthalates, phosphates, fragrances, and retinyl palmitateOrganic All-Purpose Balm made without petrolatum, phthalates, dyes, synthetic fragrances, mineral oil, and lanolinBaby Laundry Detergent made without MIT/BIT, fragrances, phthalates, optical brighteners, and SLS/SLESHow To Use:Plant-Based Baby Wipes: From diaper change duty to messy fingers - my ultra-thick, ultra-soft design gets the job done! Open my lid and remove the inner label to pull wipes. Close lid firmly after every use to keep moist, Store at room temperature. Please don't flush!Soothing Bottom Wash: Time to cleanse + refresh! I help gently clean without irritating skin, all while soothing babe's bum. Spray my refreshing formula directly onto your babe’s bottom during changes.Organic All-Purpose Balm: I'm the do-it-all balm! I'm designed to salve dry + sensitive skin. Dab me on cuticles, lips, elbows, knees, or hair for a lil' extra TLC.Baby Laundry Detergent: I'm here for those "uh-oh" moments! For medium loads, use 1/2 my bottle. For large loads, use my full bottle.Caring Caution:Plant-Based Baby Wipes: For external use only - please discontinue use if prolonged irritation or redness occurs. To avoid risk of choking or suffocation, keep away from children.Soothing Bottom Wash: Use as directed. Avoid contact with eyes. Do not spray directly into face. Keep out of reach of children except under adult supervision.Organic All-Purpose Balm: Use as directed. Keep out of reach of children except under adult supervision.Baby Laundry Detergent: Eye irritant. May be harmful if swallowed. Avoid eye contact. Avoid prolonged contact with skin. Do not swallow. If swallowed: do not induce vomiting. Call a physician or Poison Center. Eye contact: Flush with water for 15 minutes. Get medical attention if irritation persists. Skin Contact: Rinse skin with water. Get medical attention if irritation develops and persists. Keep out of reach of children and pets.

name: Love To Dream Swaddle UP Adaptive Original Swaddle Wrap
description: The Love To Dream Swaddle UP is the original & innovative swaddle that allows your baby to sleep with arms up! Babies naturally sleep with their arms up when you place them on their backs. Traditional swaddling binds their arms across their chest or at their sides. When babies wake up and want to self-soothe, they need to have access to their hands to rub their cheeks or put their hands in their mouth. This helps your baby to quickly settle & establish an easy & peaceful sleep routine. Our ergonomic shape and specifically engineered 360° stretch fabric helps reduce the risk of swaddling too tight, insuring you have the right fit for your infant. The Swaddle UP applies gentle, even pressure around the body which may help settle your baby. Most importantly, your baby stays settled and swaddled all night long - which means more sleep for you too! Available in 3 sizes - Newborn: 5-8.5 lbs., Small: 8-13 lbs., Medium: 13-19 lbs. Buy two - one to wear and one in the wash.
