name: Esembly Organic Diaper Rash Relief Cream - 3oz
description: Esembly Rash Relief Cream is a truly effective, organic, and all-natural diaper rash treatment. Our non-nano zinc oxide based cream creates a barrier between wetness and your baby’s bum, giving irritated skin the chance to heal, while soothing and relieving discomfort from diaper rash. Rash Relief Cream is only needed to treat diaper rash—check out our Everyday Balm (sold separately) for day-to-day skin protection. Esembly Rash Relief Cream is cloth diaper safe, so you can be assured that unlike most diaper balms and creams on the market, this one will wash easily and effectively out of your Esembly Inners and Outers (sold separately) or other reusable diapers.At first sign of redness or rash, apply liberally to clean, dry skin after every diaper change until irritation subsides. Continue use for 12-24 hours after rash has healed. For maximum benefit, be sure to work the balm into the skin as you would a lotion. Use only as directed. For external use only. Avoid contact with eyes. When not in use, keep tube closed and stored in a cool, dry place.

name: The Honest Company Clean Conscious Disposable Diapers Fall Vibes & Foxy Cozy Cool - (select size and Count)
description: Introducing our best diapering experience ever! New Clean Conscious Diapers are designed with safe, plant-based materials, a wetness indicator (so you know when it’s time for a fresh one), enhanced blowout protection, and advanced absorption for dry, healthy-looking booties. Plus, a secure, comfy fit for less sag + more swag.Our Clean Conscious Diapers were mindfully designed with features for each stage of your babe’s diapering journey. Grow up with Honest!What Makes A Clean Conscious Diaper?To make the core of the diaper, we harvest wood from sustainably managed pine + spruce trees in Scandinavia, which is then turned into fluff pulp at a Swedish mill using totally chlorine-free processing – aka no dioxins (toxic chemicals) in our waterwayWe don't add latex, fragrance, or parabensWe use a 100% plant-based backsheet, and our new, more efficient design reduces the amount of material used in each diaperOur diapers are cruelty-free and never tested on animalsOur diaper boxes are made from 100% PCR post recycled consumer cardboard (aka they’re 100% recyclable) – that means no new trees cut down and no landfill, if recycled How To Use:Lie your babe on their back on a safe, clean surface and gently lift them to place the diaper under their bum. Bring the diaper front over + up to your babe’s tummy and fasten the tabs securely. To minimize leaks, make sure the leg cuffs are pulled out, and not tucked in.Caring Caution: To avoid suffocation, keep this packaging away from babies + children. Choking may result from anything babies put in their mouths. To avoid the risk of choking, don’t allow babies to tear the diaper. Discard any torn or or damaged diapers. Like any piece of clothing, diapers are flammable.

name: My Tiny Moments Nursery Essential Gift Set - Buffalo Check Moose 6pc
description: Give the gift of cozy snuggles with the Buffalo Check Moose Nursery Bedding Essentials 6 Piece Gift Set by My Tiny Moments. This all in one set features two microfiber crib sheets, a flannel and faux shearling baby blanket, a 100% cotton flannel swaddle and a moose plush all bundled in a black felt storage caddy. Crib sheets fit a standard 28 in x 52 in crib mattress and have 8-inch deep pockets and are fully elasticized for a secure fit. One crib sheet features red and black Buffalo Check moose, bears, pine trees, and gray arrows and paw prints. The other crib sheet features a red and black lumberjack plaid with bear and moose silhouettes. Flannel and faux shearling baby blanket measures 30 in x 40 in. Baby Blanket is 100% brushed deluxe cotton flannel with a red and black Buffalo Check print on one side and cozy gray faux shearling on the opposite side. 100% Cotton flannel swaddle baby blanket measures 48 in x 48 in and features a directional print of mom and baby moose surrounded by mountains, trees, and clouds in traditional black, gray and white. Moose plush is light brown plush with a tan muzzle and antlers and measures 11 in. tall.Black Felt Storage Caddy features removable divider and is designed to keep diapers, wipes, and changing items organized. Felt Storage Caddy measures 11.5 in x 6 in x 8 in.

name: Burt's Bees Baby® Beekeeper™ Wearable Blanket Organic Cotton - Rugby Stripes - Pink
description: The Beekeeper is perfectly proportioned to allow the hips and legs to move freely, while keeping the head and arms outside the blanket. Designed to replace loose blankets in the crib (as recommended by the American Academy of Pediatrics), the Beekeeper keeps your little bee cozy, warm, and secure throughout the night, giving you the peace of mind to get some rest yourself.We found the best, most durable YKK zipper, and we guarantee it for life. Thoughtful protective features keep the zipper from touching baby's skin, and keep its pull out of curious little hands. It's even inverted to make those dreaded 3 a.m. diaper changes easier for you. (At least a little bit.)We only use GOTS certified organic cotton. This makes our product ideal for your little bee's sensitive skin. GOTS certification ensures that our fabric treatments fall within their strict guidelines of what is acceptable. That means we cut out the bad stuff and provide the best for your baby.We are proud to have won both the 2016 and 2017 Cribsie Award for the snuggliest and softest sleepwear! Our cotton is combed & ringspun. In short, we get rid of cotton impurities during the spinning process. The result is the softest cotton! We have done all we can to ensure baby's skin is only in contact with the highest quality, softest cotton.

description: Our changing mat is made similar to a standard yoga mat to ensure a soft and comfortable spot for your baby to rest, providing durable and comfortable convenience for on the go changes. While the changing mat may emanate a faint smell, be assured it is safe to use with your baby right out of the packaging, and the scent will dissipate in a short time. Enter the world of Ubbi where innovative products are designed and created with parents and children in mind. Under the Ubbi name, you will find unique, quality products that are easy to use, helping to simplify parents' lives while keeping babies as happy and safe as can be. Thanks to its award-winning can of steel, Ubbi is now a recognized brand worldwide. The Ubbi diaper pail is renowned for its ability to achieve maximum odor control and appreciated for offering the convenience and value of utilizing any standard trash bag or reusable cloth liner, a breakthrough in the diaper disposal market. With the same customer focused philosophy and innovative design capabilities, the Ubbi brand is now expanding its signature diapering selection and extending into the feeding category. A wide range of Ubbi branded products is now available for today's modern parents who are looking for stylish and functional baby essentials. From concept to final creation, the Ubbi team works together every step of the way to bring the best in design and value. The input of every member of the team is taken into account in the development of the Ubbi products, but consumer input is the most important as customer satisfaction is our primary goal.
